## ERROR TIPS
### Inventory full when harvesting
- Ensure that the agent's inventory has sufficient space before attempting to harvest resources.

### Errors when extracting from an invalid location
- The agent attempted to extract iron-plate from (0.0, 0.0), but there was no entity containing iron-plate at that location.
- Ensure that the target location for extraction contains the desired item and a valid entity that can provide it.
